citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:50a on
05-Oct-16.
ACI Bartels spoke with the licensee at 11:10a. The licensee stated they did not have any regulated animals and
they were out of state.
